description: Non-Material Minor Amendment to Planning Permission 2012/04066/RES dated 13th March 2013 for amendments to the internal configuration of Building F to the accommodation mix to include: One additional DMS 2 bedroom unit (11 now 12), a reduction of 3 Private 1 Bedroom units (43 now 39), increase in Private 2 bedroom by and additional 5 units (97 now 103) and an increase of one additional Private 3 bedroom unit (37 now 38) and minor changes to the external appearance.
